PRESENTATION LAYER - UI & User Interaction (lib/features/*/presentation/)
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Purpose: Handles UI rendering, user interaction, and presentation state

Components:
  • Views: Screens/pages that extend CustomGetView
  • Controllers: Business logic orchestration (plain classes) -> create functions here only
  • Presenters: Reactive state management (GetxController) -> create functions only necessary to be called on onInit and onClose or onDispose, presenters must include all the variables you need to be used in the view
  • Bindings: Dependency injection setup -> create bindings for interface and implementation of the controller, presenter, usecase, repository and datasource

Example Structure:
  features/auth/presentation/
    ├── views/
    │   └── login.dart           
    ├── controllers/
    │   ├── interface/
    │   │   └── login.controller.interface.dart
    │   └── implementation/
    │       └── login.controller.implementation.dart
    ├── presenters/
    │   ├── interface/
    │   │   └── login.presenter.interface.dart
    │   └── implementation/
    │       └── login.presenter.implementation.dart
    └── bindings/
        └── login.dart